  "body": "I found while looking at #23621 that `kubectl describe pod` does not correctly handle env vars populated by secret or configmap keys:\n\n```\nkubectl  describe pod testsecret\n\n    Environment Variables:\n      SECRET_USERNAME:\n```\n\nI think the right output here would be something like:\n\n```\nkubectl  describe pod testsecret\n<snip>\n    Environment Variables:\n      SECRET_USERNAME: <populated by key 'username' of secret 'credentials'>\n      SOME_CONFIG_VAR: <populated by key 'some-property' of configmap 'my-config'>\n```\n",
